 important centre \\u00e9conomique de la r\\u00e9gion.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"312202c\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"66.6666\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2eebeab\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/ecf-2.local\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/04\\/fakePic3.jpg\",\"id\":135,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"8e9806c\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"row\",\"flex_gap\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0},\"flex_align_items\":\"center\",\"content_width\":\"full\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a93fc7b\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"33.3333\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2d281b0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>En 1989, la R\\u00e9volution de velours a eu lieu \\u00e0 Prague, marquant la fin du r\\u00e9gime communiste en Tch\\u00e9coslovaquie. En 1993, la Tch\\u00e9coslovaquie a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 pacifiquement divis\\u00e9e en deux pays distincts, la R\\u00e9publique tch\\u00e8que et la Slovaquie, avec Prague comme capitale de la R\\u00e9publique tch\\u00e8que.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1cf98c7\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":\"66.6666\"}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"217abf0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/ecf-2.local\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/04\\/roomView.jpg\",\"id\":83,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"fc40bd6\",\"elType\":\